# AI 前端设计规范

- **Phase 1–4**：ui-ux-pro-max → pencil → Vue（`useThemeColor` / `useThemeMode`）→ impeccable audit/polish
- **Gate**：Audit ≥ 14/20，无 P0/P1，`npm run build` 通过
- **主题**：`design-system/THEME.md` · **项目名**：`design-system/PROJECT.md`（`-p` 用 displayName）
- **主编排**：`.cursor/skills/ai-frontend-design-workflow/SKILL.md`
- **Pencil**：`.cursor/skills/pencil-design-workflow/SKILL.md` · `pencil-sync.md`
- **质量**：`.cursor/skills/impeccable/SKILL.md` · `project-bridge.md`
- **Agents**：`.cursor/agents/design-director.md` · `design-inspector.md`
- **Commands**：`.cursor/commands/audit.md` · `polish.md` · `critique.md`
- **禁止**：无 Brief 大规模写 UI · 跳过 Phase 4 · 直接 Read/Grep `.pen`
- 详细规范见 `.claude/rules/ai-frontend-design.md`
